{"type": "article", "id": 27033, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-19T07:13:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27816, "name": "De-dimension"}, {"id": 27817, "name": "Fade"}, {"id": 27818, "name": "BlackFin Camper Box"}, {"id": 27819, "name": "LeeLuu"}, {"id": 27820, "name": "Kiyojo"}, {"id": 27821, "name": "Yarn Bowl"}, {"id": 27822, "name": "BiteMyApple"}, {"id": 27823, "name": "Barruntando"}, {"id": 27824, "name": "Jongha Choi"}, {"id": 27825, "name": "Fernando Mastrangelo"}, {"id": 27826, "name": "Chris Johnson"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145406JY7WLCsyupUevcSG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>De-dimension by Jongha Choi</h2>\n<p>从墙上取下一张椅子的图片，一番折叠后就变成了一把真正的椅子——这并不是电影中的场景，而是设计师 <a href=\"http://jonghachoi.com/\">Jongha Choi</a> 推出的一个设计项目，名为 De-dimension。这些颜色各异的桌椅都可以从平面变为立体，Choi 希望通过强调这个体验的过程，能让我们对图像有一个崭新的认识，而不是刻板地认为图像只能被限定在一个平面上。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111057tfd9bWK2kQRpceny.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111057j3QXNHZPqL7m5pD0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021110578wgHbmhByOkF54fP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111058bVE7DMq5jtO3vUdg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111058Sj1hvTLFo5P6qdwn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Fade by Fernando Mastrangelo</h2>\n<p>作为 <a href=\"http://www.fernandomastrangelo.com/\">Fernando Mastrangelo</a> 推出的 MMATERIAL 线的新品，Fade 是一系列有着细腻彩色层次的家具，看上去好像是将一幅幅抽象画给具象的成果。通过手工染色和逐层浇筑的方式，Mastrangelo 成功地让水泥能够呈现出水墨般渲染的效果， 打造出了这些吸引人眼球的家具表面，可以说是一次艺术与设计的完美结合。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070211105971vyYOcnPaESCWqm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67708333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111059MIDNcPVwQoBsbi0G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09895833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111059IvDG5ZCyVbduagOS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.27754237\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111100ZbG569Kj7uaNFDLR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.06567797\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111100tLTc3ua1nEF7kBhm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99895833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111101K5XwY9cW1Sk64CJ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.07708333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>BlackFin Camper Box by Black Fin Camper Box</h2>\n<p>如果你打算来一场自驾野营之旅，这个名为 <a href=\"https://blackfincamperbox.com/\">BlackFin Camper Box</a> 的帐篷或许是个不错的选择。它采用了弹出式的设计，在不超过 30 秒的时间里就能很轻松地将帐篷展开（高度约为 0.9 米），可以舒舒服服地躺进两个人。帐篷的配置也很齐全：可以调节的爬梯、防水材质、透明门帘、可以装衣物的挂钩等等户外标配一应俱全。如果你对这个时髦的帐篷感兴趣的话，可以通过 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1466134845/blackfin-camper-box-hard-shell-roof-top-tent\">Kickstarter</a> 参与众筹，早鸟价为 1695 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111101j6BshmqnfGo3H0Vr.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111102gGy0pqNcMu3rmZ9d.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111103en6apPJwQrh3ESBL.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111104xpJTtvEDW18wBgi9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111104YKdwD8s9CA7SMbpP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111105DhOFVt3BdIxw8e9b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>LeeLuu by LeeLuu Labs</h2>\n<p>抱紧怀中的小动物玩偶，它就变成了一盏散发着温柔光芒的小夜灯，而在抚摸下它的光线开始慢慢变暗，最后又变成了普通玩偶的模样——这个名为 LeeLuu 的夜灯依靠拥抱转化为能量运作，由四位来自芬兰的女设计师共同研发而成。可爱的动物造型搭配讨巧的感应式设计，真的让人很想抱着它入睡。如果你也想在 LeeLuu 的陪伴下度过漫漫长夜，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/leeluu-the-magical-touch-sensitive-nightlight--2#/\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 69 欧元（包含邮费）。美中不足的是，它只能发往美国和欧盟国家。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111105SwgkPtmioqLIGDzc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73225806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111106bLHvCjtxpKhQo38J.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111106bNy0U4wRM6InO5gk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111107e1y089v6QN7YDoT5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63870968\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111107WqYjn3QTZR0Smrzc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52916667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Kiyojo dock by Chris Johnson</h2>\n<p>Chris Johnson 为 <a href=\"http://bitemyapple.co/\">BiteMyApple</a> 设计的磁性 iPhone 架 Kiyojo 是一个希望在你因为下厨、锻炼等原因而无法顺利使用手机时解放你双手的小工具。它能够牢牢地吸附在冰箱或是其他金属表面上，所以无论是察看菜谱还是边下厨边和人 FaceTime 你都不用再手忙脚乱了。如果你对 Kiyojo 感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/bitemyapple/kiyojo-the-best-magnetic-dock-for-your-iphone-6-6s\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 59 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111109kYRamb4hxfH8iV9n.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111109nIohJPHg0l9dLZpT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111110krXgx1vVZ2wAzJBL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111110osCLTFNKDvxqAkSu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111111AnBC0Y59fZIdUa7O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111111Kzj6JofGbvn8mr2q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Yarn Bowl by Barruntando</h2>\n<p>有小动物为你“看守”毛线，连编织都变得甜蜜起来。来自西班牙的 <a href=\"http://www.barruntando.etsy.com/\">Barruntando</a> 是一个手工陶器品牌，旗下的毛线碗除了一些基本造型之外，还有设计成诸如狐狸、刺猬以及蝙蝠（这可是万圣节特别版）的款式。它们的配色都非常清新，既时尚又实用。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/es/shop/Barruntando?section_id=15068368&amp;ref=shopsection_leftnav_2\">链接</a>购买这些可爱的毛线碗，售价为 33.55 至 37.02 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111112iaI8wpzyteAhJVbR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67192785\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111113sVqv8DoAlxF0ifwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67192785\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111113TuB4ZFWxvnmcsVMw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67192785\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111113RmBn127zOLKDbPqE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67192785\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111114SWpNAaFiR6jIkqwr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67268623\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111114oQ43i6CyWI7HwDdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67192785\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}